                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;br/&gt;
Image generating&#160;overlapping text. (not every but for some krilic fonts )&lt;br/&gt;
PDFBox pdf to image generates overlapping text. (2.0.15 version and prev )&lt;/p&gt;</description>
