[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1857787&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1857787&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-4520&quot; title=&quot;PDFBox PDFToImage shows black bars on scanned text&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-4520&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-4520&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: don&apos;t render type3 fonts when text rendering mode is 3 (invisible)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16821783" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 19 Apr 2019 08:51:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1857788 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
