                            <comment id="16821827" author="sunedge" created="Fri, 19 Apr 2019 10:15:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you very much Bro.&lt;br/&gt;
It&apos;s working now.&lt;br/&gt;
I want to ask about When be maven release?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks a lot. You very help us.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16821829" author="tilman" created="Fri, 19 Apr 2019 10:21:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We just had a release. New releases are usually done every 3-4 months.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16821836" author="sunedge" created="Fri, 19 Apr 2019 10:48:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ok. We will wait new release. till that day we will use this.jar&lt;br/&gt;
Thank you very much one more time.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
